      },
      "finalAssistantVisibleText": "OPENCLAW_OUTPUT_DELTA_PROOF_83199=passed",
      "toolSummary": {
        "calls": 1,
        "tools": ["bash"],
        "failures": 0
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Redacted exported trajectory excerpt from `.openclaw/trajectory-exports/proof-83199-real/events.jsonl`:

